$ Android SDK: system-images/android-apiLevel/variant

{ variant

  *variant* corresponds to specific features implemented by the system image; possible values include
    • google_apis
    • android_wear

}

sa:
  The parent directory → development/Android/SDK/dirs/system-images/android-apiLevel[android-apiLevel]

  The subdirectory → development/Android/SDK/dirs/system-images/android-apiLevel/variant/arch[arch]
